      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh okay but i cant call a doctor at 1am lol. i'm just looking for a straight answer. if i just take a half dose of the zolpidem it should be fine right? like the amount of alcohol is so low it wouldnt even matter if i take a little bit of the pill. just tell me if a small dose is safe so i can stop worrying and sleep.",
